what have I got to confess?

26:51.740 --> 26:54.413
It's all a load of crap, anyway.
Brandi's lying through her teeth.

26:54.500 --> 26:56.252
- How do you mean?
- I've read her diary.

26:56.340 --> 26:58.092
She's been grounded for six months at home

26:58.180 --> 27:02.139
