to go drinking and taking ecstasy.

27:02.220 --> 27:04.939
And she has sex with boys
all the time in cars.

27:05.020 --> 27:07.295
She's just pretending to be holy.

27:16.100 --> 27:17.772
Vincent Timoney.

27:20.420 --> 27:22.695
