27:22.780 --> 27:24.736
So that's us even now, right?

27:26.660 --> 27:28.093
Boys?

27:32.460 --> 27:34.815
Meet Vinny.

27:34.900 --> 27:35.855
What?

27:35.940 --> 27:39.171
- How did you?
