to CID for a girl of your age.

27:56.100 --> 28:00.093
It would be very useful for me
to have a friend <i>inside</i> CID.

28:00.180 --> 28:03.695
- Just till you work off your debt, of course.
- My debt is cleared!

28:03.780 --> 28:10.458
What makes you think that a name
