30:39.180 --> 30:42.138
And they won't do it then!

30:42.220 --> 30:46.896
SHE SOBS LOUDLY

30:47.980 --> 30:50.369
(Frank) 'Dear Monica.

30:50.460 --> 30:54.248
'Dear, spoiled, up-the-duff Monica.

30:54.340 --> 30:58.731
'You're the only one in the world
who could understand.

30:58.820 --> 31:04.497
