in the world I can never tell.

31:04.580 --> 31:07.936
'I know I'm hurting you,
and I'm sorry.

31:09.540 --> 31:11.417
'But I've got no choice.'

31:14.060 --> 31:15.015
(Norma) Jesus!

31:15.100 --> 31:18.649
So I had the police round, you know?
That nice young one.

31:18.740 --> 31:21.413
Stay in the road!
Look where you're going!

31:21.500 --> 31:24.458
That's enough, that's enough, now stop!

31:24.540 --> 31:26.417
Stop! Stop the car!

31:26.500 --> 31:27.694
THUNK!

31:27.780 --> 31:29.532
- Are you all right, love?
- Fuck!

31:29.620 --> 31:33.579
- Have we finished?
- Oh, Jesus!

31:33.660 --> 31:37.016
Yes, Lillian! Oh...!

31:37.100 --> 31:39.978
We have finished permanently!

31:40.060 --> 31:42.176
Fine, I'll teach meself!

31:53.060 --> 31:54.015
She's coming.

31:57.060 --> 31:59.858
That's settled, then. We'll head out about four.

32:01.780 --> 32:03.532
What's happening at four?

32:03.620 --> 32:07.818
We're going to the... Christian youth group.

32:07.900 --> 32:09.970
Every week on the estate.

32:10.060 --> 32:11.413
Talk about the Bible.

32:13.660 --> 32:16.254
And... do activities.

32:16.340 --> 32:18.137
Christian activities.

32:18.220 --> 32:20.370
Come if you want.

32:22.100 --> 32:23.374
Suit yourself.

32:27.980 --> 32:29.493
(Rosie) 'Have you ever been? '

32:29.580 --> 32:31.935
Paris? No, no.

32:32.020 --> 32:34.215
I'm sure I will though, one day. Have you?

32:35.660 --> 32:36.979
Frank? >

32:38.060 --> 32:39.095
Hi, Norma.

32:41.180 --> 32:42.772
What you doing?

32:43.900 --> 32:45.538
I'm Norma.

32:45.620 --> 32:47.497
Sorry... Yeah, Norma...

32:47.580 --> 32:49.969
- (Norma) I'm a friend of the family.
- Rosie.

32:51.140 --> 32:53.734
So what you doing here then?

32:53.820 --> 32:57.972
I was just at the hospital
getting me nose sorted.

32:58.060 --> 33:01.097
So how's the course going, Frank?

33:01.180 --> 33:04.217
Great, yeah. Just private reading now.

33:04.300 --> 33:07.098
You don't need to explain to me.
I'm not your keeper.

33:07.180 --> 33:08.454
Yeah, I know, I'm just...

33:11.980 --> 33:13.698
It's very nice to meet you.

33:15.420 --> 33:17.934
Right, yeah, catch you later, Norma.

33:27.540 --> 33:30.691
(Frank) 'It was the beginning of the end.'

33:32.980 --> 33:34.891
Begin.

34:29.659 --> 34:32.811
Been sticking your nose in
where it doesn't belong again?

34:42.699 --> 34:44.850
Frank in late again last night?

34:46.699 --> 34:48.018
Uh-huh.

34:51.580 --> 34:53.217
You're all right about it?

34:53.300 --> 34:54.255
Course I am.

34:54.340 --> 34:56.092
You're not even curious.

34:56.179 --> 34:59.217
No. Norma, I'm not curious,
not even a little bit.

34:59.300 --> 35:02.736
