I won't let this interfere.

35:31.860 --> 35:34.533
We can't pretend
the real world in't there.

35:34.620 --> 35:38.932
Well, who gets to decide
what's real and what isn't?

35:39.020 --> 35:40.339
I want <i>this</i> to be real!

35:40.420 --> 35:45.016
You know, Norma can take Monica back.

35:45.100 --> 35:47.853
Peter's a grown lad,
he'll look after himself.

35:47.940 --> 35:49.339
