35:59.700 --> 36:01.816
Temporary until...

36:03.780 --> 36:04.929
I can't leave him.

36:06.180 --> 36:08.694
I would never leave him. He needs me.

36:08.780 --> 36:09.895
<i>I need you.</i>

36:09.980 --> 36:14.496
It doesn't mean it's over between us.
We can carry on as we've been doing.

36:14.580 --> 36:17.856
Oh, what, sneaking around?

36:17.940 --> 36:19.896
Hiding on buses, drinking bad tea?

36:19.980 --> 36:24.258
- It's better than nothing.
- Well, I don't think it is, Rosie.

36:28.380 --> 36:30.132
I can't!

36:30.220 --> 36:34.657
All my fucking life,
just scraps from the table, not now!

36:34.740 --> 36:38.096
Not the distance that we've come.
Don't you understand?

36:38.180 --> 36:42.810
I am not the same man
that I was a few days ago!

36:42.900 --> 36:44.697
What are you saying?

36:47.020 --> 36:48.453
I'm...

36:48.540 --> 36:53.978
HE BREATHES HEAVILY

36:54.060 --> 36:56.654
