37:29.340 --> 37:31.570
Oh, fuck! No!

37:31.660 --> 37:35.175
Well, that's where Peter's from,
it's familiar to him.

37:38.140 --> 37:40.096
I think we should take it.

37:48.380 --> 37:53.056
Let me travel back on the bus
with you tonight, one last time.

37:53.140 --> 37:56.337
(Frank) 'So that was it, the love of my life

37:56.420 --> 38:00.333
