don't come, make it last".'

38:11.780 --> 38:13.498
Margaret Thatcher.

38:14.460 --> 38:16.655
Vanessa Feltz.

38:19.380 --> 38:20.893
Gordon Brown.

38:24.500 --> 38:27.139
Gordon Brown shagging Vanessa Feltz.

38:29.260 --> 38:32.696
Oh, oh, oh, oh, fuck!

38:32.780 --> 38:38.491
HEAVY BREATHING, PANTING

38:38.580 --> 38:40.298
'Fucking hair trigger.

38:42.180 --> 38:43.852
'And that was it.

38:43.940 --> 38:46.170
'The end.

38:46.260 --> 38:48.854
'Anything else would have been a slow death.'

