We're not supposed to drink alcohol.

39:04.260 --> 39:07.332
Jesus did, didn't he?
Turned water into wine and stuff.

39:07.420 --> 39:12.096
Anyhow, Thessalonians 5:21 says,
"Test all things

39:12.180 --> 39:14.774
"and hold firmly that which is good."

39:23.140 --> 39:25.256
LOUD DANCE MUSIC

39:36.100 --> 39:37.692
I failed the exam.

39:37.780 --> 39:41.329
