BELL RINGS

42:15.340 --> 42:17.251
Come on, Frank, this is us.

42:24.220 --> 42:25.369
(Mimi) Nice to meet ya.

42:25.460 --> 42:29.419
...Not much of a conversationalist,
is she, your mate?

42:32.860 --> 42:35.897
Jesus, Frank!
Did you take a bath in Old Spice?

42:35.980 --> 42:39.609
Whatever happened to the days when public
transport smelt of piss and tobacco?

42:39.700 --> 42:43.090
God Almighty!

42:50.580 --> 42:54.459
(Frank) 'And that was
the last time I saw her.

42:54.540 --> 42:58.818
'Into the sunset and out of my life.

42:58.900 --> 43:03.894
'My heart sank like a condemned man
through the hangman's trap door.'

43:08.460 --> 43:09.893
Come on, Barney!

43:19.220 --> 43:21.893
All this for a week in a caravan in Filey.

43:21.980 --> 43:24.335
You're mental, Debbie.

43:26.700 --> 43:28.497
Howay!

43:29.380 --> 43:30.654
Right.

43:51.420 --> 43:53.411
LILLIAN YELLS

43:54.980 --> 43:56.095
What you doing?!

43:58.420 --> 43:59.375
Argh!

44:00.700 --> 44:03.533
TYRES SQUEAL, GLASS SMASHES

44:03.620 --> 44:05.451
POLICE SIREN WAILS

44:18.740 --> 44:20.890
What are the chances of that?

44:20.980 --> 44:22.572
< I'm choking, I can't breathe.

44:22.660 --> 44:24.810
Try and relax. Try and relax.

44:27.300 --> 44:30.451
(Frank) 'Thought I was too old
to get blind-sided,

44:30.540 --> 44:34.852
'but I suppose that's the ugly beauty
of the divine sense of humour.

44:36.340 --> 44:41.892
'AII our ifs, buts and maybes,
I mean, the sun still rises,

44:41.980 --> 44:43.732
'politicians still lie.

44:43.820 --> 44:47.495
'City continue to break my heart.

44:47.580 --> 44:50.333
'I'm just one man.

44:50.420 --> 44:51.694
'What the fuck do I matter? '

44:51.780 --> 44:53.008
Frank?

44:54.940 --> 44:55.816
What?

45:00.020 --> 45:01.772
Whatever dream you had,

45:01.860 --> 45:04.693
weren't a very happy one, were it?

45:08.100 --> 45:09.055
No.

45:12.140 --> 45:14.256
You've been a long, long way away.

45:16.540 --> 45:18.690
Thanks for coming back to us.

45:22.980 --> 45:25.130
But just a heads up -

45:25.220 --> 45:29.532
if you ever consider anything
like that ever again,

45:29.620 --> 45:33.579
I personally will neuter you
like the mangy tom that you are.

45:36.260 --> 45:39.696
Hm.
SHE SIGHS

45:40.740 --> 45:42.412
'And just like that,

45:42.500 --> 45:48.769
'me and Rosie and the tale
of our brief encounter was history.'

